               <p>Third Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1968. 
               
                  <persName id="t18311020-12-defend212" type="defendantName">
                     THOMAS 
                     DAVIS
                  <interp inst="t18311020-12-defend212" type="surname" value="DAVIS"></interp>
